data.name: Person
accesskey
data.description: Access keys allow you to query data from one of our data providers.  Find out more at http://matchbox.io.

Uses the provided information to update a person in matchbox.io.  If enough contact information is provide, such as a name and address, an email address or a web cookie, that information is used to perform a match and update the person's contact information.  If a match is not found, a new person is created within your matchbox.io account.  In addition, the entire person JSON document is returned.  The matching methodology may be modified if necessary.  Check out matchbox.io for more details.

addr_1
data.description: The first address line for the individual, if known.

data.name: addr_2
data.description: The second address line for the individual, if known.

data.name: city
data.description: The city address for the individual, if known.

data.name: city_state_zip
data.description: The city, state and zip of the address, when known.  Useful for when this information is not parsed.

data.name: cookie
data.description: Any web cookies associated with the individual.

data.name: customer_id
data.description: A unique customer identifier if used.  Must be at least 10 characters and should be unique to the person.

data.name: email
data.description: The email address of the individual, if known.

data.name: first_name
data.description: The first name of the individual, if known.

data.name: full_name
data.description: The full name of the individual, if known.  This will be parsed into individual name elements.  Parsed name information in the first_name, middle_name and last_name parameters will trump the full_name parameter when both are provided.

data.name: last_name
data.description: The last name of the individual, if known.

data.name: middle_name
data.description: The middle name of the individual, if known.

data.name: source
data.description: The source of the individual record.  All sources will be tracked in the "sources" array.

data.name: state
data.description: The state for the individual, if known.

data.name: twitter
data.description: The twitter account for the individual, if known.

data.name: zip
data.description: The zip code for the individual, if known.

description: The matchbox.io Match API identifies and deduplicates individuals by providing a consistent identifier.  By correcting spelling errors and using "fuzzy" match logic, the API can be used to track an individual across different marketing channels, including mailing, email and social.  The API can also be used to identify members of the same household and to append third party data.  Check out http://matchbox.io to find out more.
